highlights.text: Mc Gw has the most spots on Viral Songs Brazil. “SEQUÊNCIA FEITICEIRA” is the highest at #5.
“Me Postou no Daily, Festa do Big G” by lvtrainer2k is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Brazil at #7.
“P do Pecado - Ao Vivo” by Grupo Menos É Mais and Simone Mendes has been on Viral Songs Brazil the longest, at 134 days straight.
“Bem Querer / Primavera (Vai Chuva) - Ao Vivo” by Panda and MJ Records is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Brazil, up 31 spots at #44.
